ucible\\\\n+sdp/verification/t-002@20260416t043834z-verify.md:3:**Verify Agent:** Claude Sonnet 4.6 (verify)\\\\n+sdp/verification/t-002@20260416t043834z-verify.md:19:| Metric | Implementation |\\\\n+sdp/verification/t-002@20260416t043834z-verify.md:62:- Test file follows `tests/test_*.py` naming; uses `sys.path.insert` pattern consistent with other senseweave tests\\\\n+sdp/verification/t-002@20260416t043834z-verify.md:83:Tests use:\\\\n+sdp/verification/t-002@20260416t043834z-verify.md:89:Test coverage for `analyze_captured_audio` validates:\\\\n+sdp/verification/t-002@20260416t043834z-verify.md:108:2. **Document roughness duality**: Add a one-line comment at the `_audio_spectral_metrics` roughness line noting it is spectral-diff based (not psychoacoustic), to help future readers understand the intentional difference vs the tracker path.\\\\n+sdp/logs/Lead_T-008_20260408T223256Z_1775691685.log:11:Read the project's ADP documentation and understand existing patterns before making changes.\\\\n+sdp/logs/Lead_T-008_20260408T223256Z_1775691685.log:13:**ADP Phases:** Implement → Verify → Commit\\\\n+sdp/logs/Lead_T-008_20260408T223256Z_1775691685.log:15:1. Implement the fix or change described above.\\\\n+sdp/logs/Lead_T-008_20260408T223256Z_1775691685.log:41:{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"message\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2026-04-08T23:41:29.033Z\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"role\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"user\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"# Task T-008@20260408T223256Z: Add instance identity bootstrap for the R750 home: generate `instance_id`, auto-generate artistic `instance_name`, record creation metadata.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n## Acceptance Criteria\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n- First boot generates a unique UUID instance_id<br/>- Artistic name generated from word lists<br/>- Identity record persists to `~/.promptclaw/identity.json`<br/>- Subsequent boots load existing identity without regenerating\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**Tier:** T1 — Light (Bug fix / config change / minor update)\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n## Instructions\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nRead the project's ADP documentation and understand existing patterns before making changes.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**ADP Phases:** Implement → Verify → Commit\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n1. Implement the fix or change described above.\\\\\\\\n2. Ensure all existing tests pass.\\\\\\\\n3. Add a regression test if the bug was not previously caught.\\\\\\\\n4. Commit with a descriptive message: `fix(scope): short summary [T-008@20260408T223256Z]`\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n## Rules\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n- No spec required. Task description + commit message is sufficient.\\\\\\\\n- Existing tests MUST pass after your change.\\\\\\\\n- Follow existing code patterns and conventions.\\\\\\\\n- Do not modify files outside the scope of this task.\\\\\\\\n- Log any concerns to ESCALATIONS.md.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n## Validation\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nRun before committing:\\\\\\\\n```bash\\\\\\\\npip install -e '.[dev]' && pytest tests/ -x && ruff check src/ tests/ && mypy src/\\\\\\\\n```\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nAll must pass.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\"}\\\\n+sdp/logs/Lead_T-017_20260416T043834Z_1776321882.log:1:Command: gemini -p Task T-017@20260416T043834Z: Implement hook and leitmotif lifecycle management across one piece and across repertoire.\\\\n+sdp/logs/Lead_T-017_20260416T043834Z_1776321882.log:13:{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"message\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2026-04-16T06:44:45.418Z\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"role\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"user\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Task T-017@20260416T043834Z: Implement hook and leitmotif lifecycle management across one piece and across repertoire.\\\\\\\\nYour previous attempt left uncommitted changes.\\\\\\\\nCommit all required work and ensure git status is clean before exiting.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n## Acceptance Criteria\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n- hooks have class, contour, rhythm, anchor degrees, answer degrees, text hook, and timbral tags<br/>- motifs move through statement, variation, contrast, recall, answer, liquidation, and residue states<br/>- repertoire can recall a motif shape without exact self-copying<br/>- tests verify motif transformation and answer behavior\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\"}\\\\n+sdp/logs/Lead_T-017_20260416T043834Z_1776321882.log:15:{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"tool_result\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2026-04-16T06:44:56.835Z\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"tool_id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"run_shell_command_1776321895073_0\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"status\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"success\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"output\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"On branch feat/graceful-degradation\\\\\\\\nYour branch is ahead of 'origin/feat/graceful-degradation' by 12 commits.\\\\\\\\n  (use \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"git push\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" to publish your local commits)\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nChanges not staged for commit:\\\\\\\\n  (use \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"git add <file>...\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" to update what will be committed)\\\\\\\\n  (use \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"git restore <file>...\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" to discard changes in working directory)\\\\\\\\n        modified:   CHANGELOG.md\\\\\\\\n        modified:   docs/architecture.md\\\\\\\\n        modified:   docs/command-reference.md\\\\\\\\n        modified:   docs/handoff-protocol.md\\\\\\\\n        modified:   docs/startup-wizard.md\\\\\\\\n        modified:   my-claw/scripts/cypherclaw_boot.sh\\\\\\\\n        modified:   my-claw/scripts/restart_composer.sh\\\\\\\\n        modified:   my-claw/scripts/start_audio.sh\\\\\\\\n        modified:   my-claw/scripts/start_displays.sh\\\\\\\\n        modified:   my-claw/scripts/xorg-dual.conf\\\\\\\\n        modified:   my-claw/systemd/cypherclaw-sdp-runner.service\\\\\\\\n        modified:   my-claw/tools/archive_daemon.py\\\\\\\\n        modified:   my-claw/tools/audio_analysis.py\\\\\\\\n        modified:   my-claw/tools/contact_listener.py\\\\\\\\n        modified:   my-claw/tools/context_pulse.py\\\\\\\\n        modified:   my-claw/tools/dashboard_generator.py\\\\\\\\n        modified:   my-claw/tools/duet_composer.py\\\\\\\\n        modified:   my-claw/tools/gallery/fb_rende