docs/20260402-cypherclaw-embodiment-prd.md:219:- Registered as "The Scribe" sensory voice
docs/20260402-cypherclaw-embodiment-prd.md:238:- [ ] All 10 voices registered and producing data
docs/20260402-cypherclaw-embodiment-prd.md:241:- [ ] Cross-modal confidence scoring works across all voice combinations
docs/20260402-cypherclaw-embodiment-prd.md:286:- [ ] All 10 sensory voices active and visible on both monitors
docs/20260402-cypherclaw-embodiment-prd.md:298:**Key principle:** The plugin architecture (Phase 1) is foundational. Nothing else works without it. Build the democracy of senses first, then give the system its face, its voice, and its ability to listen.
